Test Pyramid:
Shows number of tests at each level
Base = unit tests, top = UI tests; more unit, fewer UI
70% unit, 20% integration, 10% UI

Test Strategy:
High-level testing plan
Defines approach, scope, types of testing, tools, and framework
Manual + Automation + Regression approach

Test Plan:
Detailed document for a project
Specifies what to test, how, who, when, and entry/exit criteria
Includes test scope, schedule, resources, test cases, and deliverables

